description:
This map contains the locations of CityRacks installed by the New York City Department of
Transportation (NYCDOT) throughout the five boroughs of New York from 1996 through the present.
This dataset will be updated on a periodic basis as new racks are installed. This data currently contains
the locations of 8940 racks installed in 7366 locations.
